room_title: Escape room "The Estate" by Maine Escape Games in South Portland
room_address: 125 John Roberts Rd, Suite 8 South Portland, ME 04106
room_description: A daring robbery has just occurred at Baldwin Manor and now an expensive piece of artwork is missing. You and your team must find clues and solve a series of puzzles to find the painting, discover who the thieves are, and escape the room within one hour.
